data.description:
Welcome to 615 Moore Loop in Byhalia, a stunning one-level home nestled on approximately 1.54 acres. This beautiful house boasts a spacious great room with wide plank LVP flooring, gas fireplace, and plenty of natural light, creating an inviting and warm ambiance. The kitchen features an oversized central island with a convenient breakfast/snack bar, overlooking both the great room and dining area.
Discover comfort in the master bedroom, complete with a private master bath featuring double sinks, a separate tub, and shower, not to mention the huge closet with wood shelving. The  floor plan splits each of the 3 bedrooms providing privacy for everyone, as well as an additional full bath and a convenient half bath adjacent to the laundry room. Smooth ceilings and an abundance of canned lighting, create a modern and bright atmosphere. Step outside to a delightful patio at the back of the home. This property harmoniously combines style, functionality, and the tranquility of country living. Built in 2020, this residence offers contemporary living with thoughtful design elements. Don't miss the opportunity to make 615 Moore Loop your dream home.
